Package: spocc
Title: R interface to many species occurrence data sources
Description: A programmatic interface to many species occurrence data sources,
    including GBIF, BISON, iNaturalist, VertNet, and more as they sources
    become easily available.
Version: 0.0.4
License: CC0
Date: 2013-12-13
